{"tid":2223851,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"[非批鬥，為研究] 唔諗住10.1去遊行嘅理由收集處","createTime":"2020-09-30T06:21:13.000Z","updateTime":"2020-10-12T06:15:02.000Z","uid":258706,"like":4,"dislike":5,"uniUserReply":18,"replies":[{"pid":"720356057b59fe9d97e7379a5a14cc8bb148f327","tid":2223851,"uid":258706,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-30T06:21:13.000Z","msg":"自8月開始，各場遊行嘅人數愈嚟愈少<br />\n想問一問<span class=\"gold\">本身有去開遊行但唔想去10.1遊行</span>嘅人，你哋今次唔諗住去嘅理由係咩？ <br />\n<br />\neg 覺得遊行冇用、怕被濫捕、唔想曬、同一條路綫已行到悶&hellip;&hellip;<br />\n<br />\nPS <span class=\"pink\">唔係想喺呢度搞批鬥，只係想研究吓大家嘅心態轉變</span> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n幫助日後各行動搞手<span class=\"brown\">決定搞乜行動、制定日後行動內容</span>，避免浪費人力物力"},{"pid":"cd13bb15dc68beec267723edd650f3648e1be8aa","tid":2223851,"uid":273218,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-09-30T06:23:47.000Z","msg":"樓主有無睇過71 果日咩環境"},{"pid":"324f5be4e25114a808839a56dd16bdd1a448e971","tid":2223851,"uid":258706,"like":1,"dislike":2,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"cd13bb15dc68beec267723edd650f3648e1be8aa","tid":2223851,"uid":273218,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-09-30T06:23:47.000Z","msg":"樓主有無睇過71 果日咩環境"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-09-30T06:25:37.000Z","msg":"個日係乜環境同一個人想唔想出冇必然關係喎<br />\n<br />\neg 一個人可以唔怕圍捕但覺得遊行冇用所以唔想再去<br />\n<br />\n所以先要研究"},{"pid":"5e6bafc02fda33feb4fafc385665e316e4fe086a","tid":2223851,"uid":74918,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-09-30T06:41:04.000Z","msg":"你研究嘅目的係咩？"},{"pid":"b458c0663edfc7f8e0b43bccbdbff11cc94e6ac2","tid":2223851,"uid":316612,"like":1,"dislike":3,"score":-2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-09-30T06:42:11.000Z","msg":"我一定唔會去，因為我恥與投共派為伍<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/no.